reviews.review_text: Two of the male employees were really nice and patient in answering my questions and getting what I needed yesterday. Customer service was fantastic

Great experience at this Mark s location. Clean, bright interior and everything is well-stocked. I was looking for women s work gloves and hiking boots, and Brett gave an outstanding customer service. This will be our go-to Mark s from now on!
I bought some sandals online but they were too big. I went down to the store with them and exchanged them quickly for a pair that fit.
They didnt have the boots I was looking for, but the staff was very helpful, friendly, and patient.

Very helpful staff, absolute great customer service: bought a pair of timberland waterproof work boots like 2 and half months prior using  em, turned out to be defective (water leaking in ) after a couple of uses and the guys were able to credit me the whole amount I paid for them; this way I could get a new pair Recommended for all your work wear needs hands down
Very friendly service. And one time I forgot a to save my receipt that I needed for work and Mathew was very helpful getting me a copy.

Awesome customer service! Whoever the manager was she deserves a raise. My boots tore after 8 months of use and she did all she could to rectify the issue. I will happily shop there knowing there are great staff who are willing to help. Thank you (I wish I knew your name) for helping me, I truly appreciate it. Friendly staff and great service. Another happy customer.

This is my absolute favourite Marks location! Matthew was amazing with helping me find the right item - by far one of the best customer service experiences Ive had. The staff work especially hard to keep the place as organized as it is and it shows.

Marks. North Van on Marine. Good selection. They are having a sale for pretty much all items. I bought some items in preparation of Christmas. There were people in the store and the cash register staff were able to move people quickly so the wait time was about 30seconds.  The emailed me the receipt and it was correct. I spent just over $100 and saved $20 from the sale prices.

I had a great experience shopping at this location. Chris was very helpful and went above and beyond for helping me out and finding what I needed. I was looking for a shoe size that was not availible on the sales floor and asked if they had any out back in the storage. After finding out they did not have it at their store, he looked at the other North Vancouver location for me and called them to confirm so he could save me the drive. After finding out that they were out as well (Even though the system showed that they had 1)  Chris placed an order for me where it was shipped to my house 2 days after the purchus date. Great customer service Chris, I appriciate it and will be back at this store again. Thank you Marks Marine Drive and Chris for your outstanding customer service! Al

The young staff member was awesome, Marks prices are great, the quality is top notch!  Their winter sale is 70% off!  Their free socks coupon one Christmas,  many years ago is a fun memory for my family

Excellent store for well built non-frill clothing. Work pants, work jackets and boots. Suited for all inclement weather. The staff are really helpful. If they dont have your size, they will do their utmost to source it from another location. Pricing is reasonable for the quality. Definitely worth a look.
The best customer service I have ever had in a marks ever!!! A manager named Marley helped me find the perfect boots! Will shop here forever, even though its a little bit ot of my way.

Ok.  You live in Vancouver.  You have a kid and you need a decent rain jacket.  Well, not all locations have them but some carry all sizes of the Viking coats.  They are inexpensive and last for years.   Mark s is seriously underrated in my opinion.  Consider them for general purpose as well as winter gear.  Decent store and they are all over the place.
Chris was helping me pick out shoes. Never had someone look after me and help me find the right shoes. He even went out of his way to find the shoes I wanted and put it on hold for me.
Great place. Always have good quality products if only the prices were friendly.

No complaints here. I walked into the store I was nicely greeted by staff.  There was a great selection of work boots.  Rohit a very nice gentleman at this store was very helpful and kind.   Great experience.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Were happy your experience with us was great. Thanks for your review Justin!
